Search Results for

    Class TSqlParserBaseListener

    This class provides an empty implementation of ITSqlParserListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.

    Inheritance
    object
    TSqlParserBaseListener
    Implements
    ITSqlParserListener
    IParseTreeListener
    Inherited Members
    object.Equals(object)
    object.Equals(object, object)
    object.GetHashCode()
    object.GetType()
    object.MemberwiseClone()
    object.ReferenceEquals(object, object)
    object.ToString()
    Namespace: SQLParser.Parsers.TSql
    Assembly: SQLParser.dll
    Syntax
    [CLSCompliant(false)]
public class TSqlParserBaseListener : ITSqlParserListener, IParseTreeListener
